arStrings.szText: To self. Groggy/waking up. At the end of the line, realization dawns--this portal belongs to Mephisto, and you aren't happy to see him.
What does that fiend want from me, now of all times?
Annoyed, to self--We just had a touching scene where our friend Donan faced his inner grief, and Mephisto showing up here is almost desecrating the moment
